steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitapi008" and Comment "Testing defect - check column type file not display in request params of GET list Api"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitapi008" display
When I add new column with Name "file" Type "file" for Table name "jitapi008"
When I check radio button popup Name "Single file"
When I check radio button popup Name "Image (PNG, JPG, JPEG, GIF, HEIC, HEIF)"
When I press Add column button popup
Then I should see column with name "file" and index "4" of table name "jitapi008" has type "file" display
